[Name] ickle
[Summary] An ICQ2000 client using the GTK-- graphical toolkit.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] ickle is an ICQ2000 client using the GTK-- graphical toolkit. It aims to bring all the useful features of ICQ2000 to non-Windows users. It supports message/URL/SMS sending/receiving (including SMS delivery reports), status changes, reading away messages, and fetching advanced user info from a server. History browsing and lots of configurability in Settings are available.
[Homepage] http://ickle.sourceforge.net/
